scene.message:
Maki: Oh, Elly!{nl}
So happy to see you!{nl}
You doing okay?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: ...{wait_fr:32}Maki?{nl}
When did you get out?{waitkey}{clearbox}Oh, but now's not the{nl}
time for that. I'm glad{nl}
everyone is safe.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Yes...{wait_fr:21}{nl}
I checked around, but{nl}
all the passages below{nl}
are blocked.{waitkey}{clearbox}There's really no way{nl}
out of town.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: It's dangerous here!{nl}
Don't worry,{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll sort it out in{nl}
a jiffy — wait somewhere{nl}
safe till then!{waitkey}{clearbox}Trust me!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: It's not safe{nl}
to be alone out here!{waitkey}{clearbox}Shouldn't you go{nl}
somewhere safe?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I know...{waitkey}{nl}
But I might as well{nl}
explore the town a bit.{nl}
Take care, everyone.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Thank you, but{nl}
I'm fine alone.{nl}
Goodbye.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Oh yeah, a lot.{nl}
It's a long story, but{nl}
basically...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Oh really...?{nl}
I can't believe I missed{nl}
out on all that!{waitkey}{clearbox}But there's still time.{nl}
I still have plenty of{nl}
chances!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey, {ctl07:1} — won't{nl}
you bring me along?{nl}
I have things I want{nl}
to investigate.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Here's a gun for{nl}
you, Kirishima.{waitkey}{clearbox}...I'm reluctant to arm{nl}
a lady, but given{nl}
the emergency,{nl}
it can't be helped.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Mark, you should've{nl}
gone somewhere else!{waitkey}Honestly, Elly's way{nl}
better than you.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: The subway is blocked.{nl}
There's no escaping{nl}
this town.{waitkey}{ret}
